{
    "plugins": [
        "@semantic-release/commit-analyzer",
        [
            "@semantic-release/release-notes-generator",
            {
                "preset": "conventionalcommits",
                "writerOpts": {
                    "headerPartial": "## declix-bash {{#if isPatch~}} <small>\n  {{~/if~}} {{version}}\n  {{~#if title}} \"{{title}}\"\n  {{~/if~}}\n  {{~#if date}} ({{date}})\n  {{~/if~}}\n  {{~#if isPatch~}} </small>\n  {{~/if}}\n\nThis is the {{version}} release of declix-bash - Bash script generator for declarative Linux system configuration.\n\n## Installation\n\n### Using Container (Recommended - No local installation required)\n\n```bash\n# Generate script using the official container\npodman run --rm -v ./resources.pkl:/work/resources.pkl ghcr.io/declix/declix-bash:{{version}} /work/resources.pkl > generated.sh\n\n# Or use 'latest' tag\npodman run --rm -v ./resources.pkl:/work/resources.pkl ghcr.io/declix/declix-bash:latest /work/resources.pkl > generated.sh\n\n# Apply the generated configuration\nbash generated.sh check   # Check what would change\nbash generated.sh diff    # Show detailed differences\nbash generated.sh apply   # Apply configuration\n```\n\n### Download Single-File Release\n\n```bash\n# Download the script\ncurl -L -o declix-bash.sh https://github.com/declix/declix-bash/releases/download/{{version}}/declix-bash.sh\nchmod +x declix-bash.sh\n\n# Or with wget\nwget https://github.com/declix/declix-bash/releases/download/{{version}}/declix-bash.sh\nchmod +x declix-bash.sh\n```\n\n### Usage Examples\n\n```bash\n# Using container (no pkl installation required)\npodman run --rm -v ./resources.pkl:/work/resources.pkl ghcr.io/declix/declix-bash:{{version}} /work/resources.pkl | bash -s apply\n\n# Using downloaded script (requires pkl installed)\n./declix-bash.sh resources.pkl | bash -s check\n./declix-bash.sh resources.pkl | bash -s diff\n./declix-bash.sh resources.pkl | bash -s apply\n```\n\n### Requirements\n\n**For container usage**: Only podman or docker\n\n**For single-file script**: \n- pkl (Apple's configuration language) must be installed\n- sudo access for system modifications\n\n"
                }
            }
        ],
        [
            "@semantic-release/exec",
            {
                "publishCmd": "echo 'Release artifacts already prepared in out/'"
            }
        ],
        [
            "@semantic-release/github",
            {
                "assets": [
                    {
                        "path": "out/declix-bash.sh",
                        "name": "declix-bash.sh",
                        "label": "declix-bash {{version}} - Single-file executable"
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    ],
    "tagFormat": "${version}",
    "preset": "conventionalcommits"
}